sentences: beginning a solo career with his 2006 LP, Toby Love, released on Sony Records.
In 2008, he received four nominations to the Billboard Latin Music Awards for songs included in his debut album.
Love won awards for two categories, Tropical Airplay Song of the Year, and Latin Rap / Hip Hop Album of the Year.
